title: Heavy Work Bench
info: The Heavy Work Bench is a crafting station used to make the Stone Slab, Sandstone Slab, Copper Plating, Tin Plating, text statues, critter statues, Gem Locks, and Trapped Chests. It is not an upgrade for the standard Work Bench, nor does it qualify as a flat surface item for NPC housing.
